response.overview: *SHUNK* is a film about cannibals and makes fun of naiveté, betrayal, and revenge. It takes place in a diner where people eat food – that, unbeknownst to them, is made of human flesh! It’s just another regular, working day until a drifter enters through the front door to stir things up for Pops and the other staff members. We follow Maggy as she’s hired to work as a waitress, and when the diner closes and the doors lock, she must fight her way through and trust her gut before the cannibals eat her heart out!
response.title: *SHUNK*
